    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>清除你的敌人。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >疯狂吸尘器(Roombattle) 是一款亲民的格斗游戏，玩家将控制配有气球的锋利武器的吸尘器。为了获胜，你必须戳破别的玩家的气球，成为最后的幸存者！除了战斗，游戏还包含大量的迷你游戏。和别的玩家互动，定制你的吸尘器，准备在不同的房间中战斗，争取胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有趣的吸尘器战斗 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与朋友们在多彩且充满活力的房间中进行刺激的吸尘器战斗。每个主题都有独特的机制，使每一轮都独特而令人兴奋。破坏房间，然后再清理！在多轮比赛中竞争，通过戳破对手的气球来消灭他们，确保胜利。收集增强道具，成为房间中最强大的吸尘器，击败别的玩家的吸尘器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223000/extras/38511db55c56ca3ee52c3fbd96dd2018.poster.avif?t=1772107011\" width=1170 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223000/extras/38511db55c56ca3ee52c3fbd96dd2018.webm?t=1772107011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223000/extras/38511db55c56ca3ee52c3fbd96dd2018.mp4?t=1772107011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>人人都能玩 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >疯狂吸尘器(Roombattle) 为所有类型的玩家设计，只需两个按键和一个操纵杆即可玩。如果没有手柄？没问题 你也可以使用键盘来玩！而且，如果你的人数超过 4 人，也不用担心 疯狂吸尘器(Roombattle) 支持最多 6 名玩家参与。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战斗 + 小游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个人都喜欢战斗 但也喜欢娱乐。为什么不将两者结合起来呢？享受带有迷你游戏的战斗吧！赢得迷你游戏回合以获得神秘技能。有了这样的力量，下一轮将会轻而易举！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223000/extras/4fc0763ffeb340e8b3143729dba19c0e.poster.avif?t=1772107011\" width=1170 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223000/extras/4fc0763ffeb340e8b3143729dba19c0e.webm?t=1772107011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223000/extras/4fc0763ffeb340e8b3143729dba19c0e.mp4?t=1772107011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>定制你的吸尘器</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海盗吸尘器？独角兽吸尘器？在 Roombattle 中，一切皆有可能！每位玩家都可以定制自己的吸尘器，并通过多种选项使其独一无二。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223000/extras/4532d39925a2382d6b4084538e01cbb8.poster.avif?t=1772107011\" width=1170 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223000/extras/4532d39925a2382d6b4084538e01cbb8.webm?t=1772107011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223000/extras/4532d39925a2382d6b4084538e01cbb8.mp4?t=1772107011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
